{"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradio"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSRadio","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio"},{"text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely radio, without labels, texts nor icons radios components","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a radio with additional texts and icon, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/90c467-radio-button","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Since","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isError:)"],"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/body"],"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSRadioItem":{"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some radios components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a radio with only an indicator, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifi